    {
        "content": "<p>the item tree will contain unexpanded <code>TypeRef</code>s, right? so you can't expand in place anyway. I'd probably make it <code>&amp;TypeRef -&gt; TypeRef</code>?</p>",
        "id": 234061722,
        "sender_full_name": "Florian Diebold",
